title: 10-8 Athlete of the Week: Samantha Shulman
text: Updated: 10/12 12:13 pm Reno, Nev. (MyNews4.com & KRNV) -- The News 4 Athlete of the Week is... Sammi Shulman!Shulman is a senior at Galena high school, who's on two competitive cheer teams that compete all over the United States.Before cheering Shulman was a competitive gymnast for 6 years. Her first year cheering, her team made it to the world championships in Florida. Because of her efforts she will be taking an offical visit to Baylor University in the coming weeks, an opportunity she never that would happen... See why in the attached clip!
